{"tid":2183628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有動物都是平等的，但有些動物比其他動物更加平等。—《動物農莊》","createTime":"2020-09-01T04:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T07:42:20.000Z","uid":32126,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d5e20c3e241e9d50849802b0e8c8ec49647d5a44","tid":2183628,"uid":32126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:55:13.000Z","msg":"事源前排拍片搵素材先見到《動物農莊》。<br />\n<br />\n睇完之後發現,咁多年來共產主義嘅歷史都冇變過。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家無睇過動物農莊,可以睇一睇我哋拍嘅尼條片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WVL9AVJKbRw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWVL9AVJKbRw&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7uojXYTbvVfDxiGm1goFu7E%3D&h=be21cf19\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WVL9AVJKbRw</a><br />\n<br />\n因為細個好鍾意當年今日尼種題材嘅節目，<br />\n<br />\n所以就自己都拍翻套類似嘅冷知識影片。<br />\n<br />\n做到上個星期講到《動物農莊》，<br />\n<br />\n再睇翻今日我哋所面對嘅一切，<br />\n<br />\n個故事當年係諷刺蘇聯，<br />\n<br />\n但到今日都係一樣，我哋嘅歷史好似不斷重複咁。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄話香港從來都無三權分立⋯<br />\n<br />\n一切嘅內容同動物農莊一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n「All animals are equal but some animals are more equal than others.」<br />\n<br />\n這，就是豬群們的平等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油！"},{"pid":"3639df12eef66de749014195ddd39986260d3c4d","tid":2183628,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:56:35.000Z","msg":"動物農莊，1984<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339362fca41d85ad086d0076857909f7b1449f15","tid":2183628,"uid":285559,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:59:59.000Z","msg":"不嬲覺得animal farm比1984係更勁嘅神作 簡單易明<br />\n<br />\nBoxer簡直係好鍾意返工嘅港豬"},{"pid":"78fc0d3601e820ddd9e2a7e9bfb8d150bcf227d6","tid":2183628,"uid":25316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:59:59.000Z","msg":"美麗新世界<br />\n我們<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196c1052213c2ec991cfba876a069a394cf5802c","ti