bnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AgjKZh.jpg&h=6fe59ebe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc8b42fc4af26cd57c8067e4f6dfc49a0013552f","tid":2183628,"uid":32126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:33:14.000Z","msg":"喬治&middot;奧威爾於1943年11月至1944年2月間創作本書，<br />\n<br />\n當時英國同蘇聯是戰時盟友，<br />\n<br />\n而英國的百姓和知識分子都對斯大林評價很高，這一現象讓奧威爾十分厭惡。<br />\n<br />\n本書的手稿，起初被許多英美出版商拒絕出版。<br />\n<br />\n但本書問世以後獲得了巨大的成功，其部分原因是由於原<br />\n<br />\n來同英國是戰時盟友的蘇聯與西方世界開始了冷戰。<br />\n<br />\n《時代雜誌》將《動物莊園》評選為1923-2005年100佳<br />\n<br />\n英文小說；它亦在20世紀百大英文小說中排第31位。<br />\n<br />\n它在1996年贏得追頒雨果獎，此外也包括在西方世界偉大著作名單之上。"},{"pid":"dfc77236a540898d9832ef8ceab276c56bc2f848","tid":2183628,"uid":54930,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/40/62/c5/4062c5e3e251cd68ca613e783cffbdeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F40%2F62%2Fc5%2F4062c5e3e251cd68ca613e783cffbdeb.jpg&h=6947c991&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9dc296a9deddf15fb321bf776bec27fd8fac132","tid":2183628,"uid":32126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dfc77236a540898d9832ef8ceab276c56bc2f848","tid":2183628,"uid":54930,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/40/62/c5/4062c5e3e251cd68ca613e783cffbdeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F40%2F62%2Fc5%2F4062c5e3e251cd68ca613e783cffbdeb.jpg&h=6947c991&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n凡兩條腿行走的都是敵人"},{"pid":"daa8bbc467c1ca7796c890079aa637d884d4a65c","tid":2183628,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9dc296a9deddf15fb321bf776bec27fd8fac132","tid":2183628,"uid":32126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dfc77236a54089